msgid "0:こずぴぃの話を聞いて、僕は首をひねった。[%p]"
msgstr "0:Something in Kozupii's story made me curious.[%p]"

msgid "100:その男はいったい何者なんだろう。[linebreak]メッセージボードを持ったホームレス。[%p]"
msgstr "100:Who was that man? A homeless man with a big sign...[%p]"

msgid "200:そう言えば僕も何度か見かけたことがあるような……。[linebreak]あれって全部同一人物だったかな？[%p]"
msgstr "200:It felt like I'd seen him a few times before, too. Were they the same person?[%p]"

msgid "300:分からないのは、そんなホームレスのおっさんがどうしてディソードのことを知っているのかっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "300:What I couldn't figure out is how the guy would know about the Di-Swords.[%p]"

msgid "400:もしかして僕がなにも知らなかっただけで、実はディソードは日本じゃメジャーな存在だったりするのかな？[%p]"
msgstr "400:Maybe the Di-Swords were famous in Japan, and I just didn't know it?[%p]"

msgid "500:……そんなわけないよな。[%p]"
msgstr "500:No, there was no way.[%p]"

msgid "600:こずぴぃの様子を窺う。[%p]"
msgstr "600:I looked over at Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "700:さっき、殺すとか物騒なことを口走ったとは思えないくらい、穏やかな表情をしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "700:Her expression was so calm and peaceful, it was hard to believe she'd been talking about killing people a moment ago.[%p]"

msgid "800:ディソードの表面に指をそっと滑らせている。[%p]"
msgstr "800:She ran her fingers softly along the surface of the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "900:[name]梢[line]「そう言えば、あのおじしゃん、別れ際にこんなこと言ってたのら」[%p]"
msgstr "900:[name]梢[line]Actually, he'd said something else just before I left.[%p]"

msgid "1000:[name]梢[line]「“君たちは特別な存在だ”」[%p]"
msgstr "1000:[name]梢[line]You're all special.[%p]"

msgid "1100:[name]梢[line]「“中でも一番特別なのは”」[%p]"
msgstr "1100:[name]梢[line]But the most special of you all…[%p]"

msgid "1200:[name]梢[line]「“その目だれの目？を産み落とした少年”」[%p]"
msgstr "1200:[name]梢[line]is the boy who coined the phrase, “Whose eyes are those?”[%p]"

msgid "1300:[name]梢[line]「らしいんだってー」[%p]"
msgstr "1300:[name]梢[line]That's what he'd said.[%p]"

msgid "1400:絶句する。[%p]"
msgstr "1400:I was stunned.[%p]"

msgid "1500:なんだ、それ……。[%p]"
msgstr "1500:What did that mean?[%p]"

msgid "1600:[name]梢[line]「んん？\u3000西條くん、心当たりあーるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "1600:[name]梢[line]Hmm? Nishijo, do you know what he meant?[%p]"

msgid "1700:[name]拓巳[line]「え？\u3000いや、別に……」[%p]"
msgstr "1700:[name]拓巳[line]Huh? Uh, no...[%p]"

msgid "1800:[name]梢[line]「ウソらー。心は正直なんだよ。西條くんは今、もんのすごーく関係ありまーすって考えてる」[%p]"
msgstr "1800:[name]梢[line]You're lying, rah! Your mind's telling the truth. Just now you were thinking that you knew exactly what he meant![%p]"

msgid "1900:くそっ、やっぱり筒抜けなのはやりにくい……。[%p]"
msgstr "1900:Crap... It's hard when somebody knows your every thought.[%p]"

msgid "2000:[name]梢[line]「なんかこわーい顔になってるー」[%p]"
msgstr "2000:[name]梢[line]Your face looks really scary![%p]"

msgid "2100:[name]梢[line]「“その目だれの目？”って、西條くんが最初にかんがーえたの？」[%p]"
msgstr "2100:[name]梢[line]Were you the one who first thought up, “Whose eyes are those?”[%p]"

msgid "2200:僕は唇を噛んで、立ち上がった。[%p]"
msgstr "2200:I bit my lip and stood up.[%p]"

msgid "2300:鼻に詰めたティッシュを抜く。鼻血は止まっていた。[%p]"
msgstr "2300:I pulled out the tissues I'd stuffed in my nose. The blood had stopped.[%p]"

msgid "2400:こずぴぃが首を傾げて見上げてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "2400:Kozupii was looking up at me confused.[%p]"

msgid "2500:[name]梢[line]「どこへ……」[%p]"
msgstr "2500:[name]梢[line]Where are you going?[%p]"

msgid "2600:僕、帰るよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "2600:I-I'm going home.[%p]"

msgid "2700:[name]梢[line]「ふえぇ！？」[%p]"
msgstr "2700:[name]梢[line]Fweh?![%p]"

msgid "2800:まだ脇腹は痛かったけど、僕はエスカレーターやエレベータは使わずに、階段を使って１階まで降りた。おかげで人混みを避けて外に出ることができた。[%p]"
msgstr "2800:My side still hurt, but I walked down the stairs instead of using the escalator or the elevator. That way, I was able to avoid the crowds on my way out.[%p]"

msgid "2900:こずぴぃが泣きそうな顔をしながら、遠慮がちについてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "2900:Kozupii followed me hesitantly at a distance, looking like she was about to cry.[%p]"

msgid "3000:[name]梢[line]「あのあのー」[%p]"
msgstr "3000:[name]梢[line]Um... Um...[%p]"

msgid "3100:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃ、なにか怒らせるよーうなこと、言ったかなー？」[%p]"
msgstr "3100:[name]梢[line]Did Kozupii say something to make you angry?[%p]"

msgid "3200:こずぴぃの問いかけは無視し、僕は頭の中で必死に考えを巡らせた。[%p]"
msgstr "3200:I ignored Kozupii's question and tried my hardest to think.[%p]"

msgid "3300:こずぴぃが会ったっていう、そのホームレスのこと。『将軍』の仲間か？[linebreak]どうして“その目だれの目？”なんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3300:This homeless man that Kozupii had met. Was he working with Shogun? Otherwise, why would he bring up, “Whose eyes are those?”[%p]"

msgid "3400:“その目だれの目？を産み落とした少年”って誰のことだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3400:Who was the boy they were talking about who'd created, “Whose eyes are those?”[%p]"

msgid "3500:僕？[%p]"
msgstr "3500:Me?[%p]"

msgid "3600:いや、違う。[linebreak]僕は“特別な少年”なんかじゃない。勇者じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "3600:No. That couldn't be right. I wasn't a special boy. I wasn't a hero.[%p]"

msgid "3700:だってディソードを手に入れられなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "3700:I couldn't even get the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "3800:ただの凡人。村人Ａだ。そうでありたい。特別になんかなりたくない。もう二度と、Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴであったようなことはゴメンだ。[%p]"
msgstr "3800:I wanted to be just an ordinary person. An NPC, even. I didn't want to be special. I never wanted to go through anything like what happened at O-FRONT again.[%p]"

msgid "3900:じゃあ、その“少年”って誰だ？[%p]"
msgstr "3900:But then who was he talking about?[%p]"

msgid "4000:考えられるのは、ニュージェネ事件の真犯人……『将軍』だ。[%p]"
msgstr "4000:I could think of only one possibility: the true NewGen killer, Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "4100:『将軍』はどう見ても老人だけど、声や背格好はむしろ少年に近いし、明らかに普通じゃない。あいつは“特別”だ。[%p]"
msgstr "4100:He might've looked like an old man, but he had the voice and figure of a young boy. And there was something clearly weird about him, too. He was special.[%p]"

msgid "4200:６件起きているニュージェネ事件のうち２件で登場する“その目だれの目？”というメッセージ。[%p]"
msgstr "4200:Two of the six NewGen cases had involved the message, “Whose eyes are those?”[%p]"

msgid "4300:僕も自分の脳内だけでよく使っていた言葉。[%p]"
msgstr "4300:It was a phrase I'd only ever used in my head.[%p]"

msgid "4400:この何気ない言葉に、いったいなにがあるっていうんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "4400:What could this seemingly innocuous phrase mean?[%p]"

msgid "4500:そこに『将軍』が僕を執拗に狙う理由も隠されてるの？[%p]"
msgstr "4500:Did it hide the reason that Shogun was after me?[%p]"

msgid "4600:探すべきなのかな、そのホームレスの男を。今もこの街のどこかにいるはずだ。相変わらず訳の分からないメッセージが書かれたボードを持って。[%p]"
msgstr "4600:Should I try looking for that homeless man? He should be somewhere in this city. He was probably still carrying the sign with the weird message on it, too.[%p]"

msgid "4700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "4700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "4800:探して、どうする？[%p]"
msgstr "4800:What would I do if I found him?[%p]"

msgid "4900:僕は立ち止まった。[linebreak]それから、自分の考えを否定するように首を振る。[%p]"
msgstr "4900:I stopped. And then I shook my head and rejected the idea.[%p]"

msgid "5000:探したからどうなるって言うんだ。[linebreak]むしろ自分から危険に飛び込むことになるかもしれないのに。[%p]"
msgstr "5000:What good would it do to find him? I might just be putting myself in more danger.[%p]"

msgid "5100:その男が『将軍』の手下で、これは僕を誘い込むための罠かもしれないんだぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "5100:He might be one of Shogun's servants, trying to lure me into a trap.[%p]"

msgid "5200:のこのことその男に会いに行って、またクエストが始まっちゃったりしたらどうするつもりだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5200:What if I went to find the guy and triggered another “quest”?[%p]"

msgid "5300:もうこの間みたいな恐怖や苦しみはうんざりだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5300:I'd experienced more than enough fear and pain already.[%p]"

msgid "5400:こずぴぃだってそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "5400:It was probably the same for Kozupii.[%p]"

msgid "5500:こずぴぃが今、このタイミングで僕に心の声で話しかけてきたのはどうして？[%p]"
msgstr "5500:Why had she come to me, with the ability to speak directly into my mind, right now?[%p]"

msgid "5600:彼女も優愛みたいに『将軍』の指示で僕に近づいてきたかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "5600:Maybe she was like Yua, and taking orders from Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "5700:殺すとか、半殺しとか、物騒なことを言うところからすると、もしかするとニュージェネの共犯ってことも考えられる。[%p]"
msgstr "5700:From all that stuff she'd said about killing—or almost killing—people, she might even be involved with the NewGen murders.[%p]"

msgid "5800:Ｏ－ＦＲＯＮＴでの騒動の後、梨深は忽然と消えた。いっさい連絡が来なくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "5800:And Rimi had disappeared after the incident at O-FRONT. She'd stopped contacting me.[%p]"

msgid "5900:あやせも自殺未遂を起こして入院中。[linebreak]七海は無事だったけど、僕の味方だった２人はいなくなった。[%p]"
msgstr "5900:Ayase was in the hospital after a failed suicide attempt. Nanami was safe, but the two people who were my allies were gone.[%p]"

msgid "6000:梨深が帰ってくるっていう保証はある？[%p]"
msgstr "6000:Was there any guarantee that Rimi would come back?[%p]"

msgid "6100:そもそも梨深はホントに“最近は学校を休んでいる”だけなの？[%p]"
msgstr "6100:Was it even true that she'd just stopped coming to school?[%p]"

msgid "6200:僕はそのことをこずぴぃからしか聞いてない。[%p]"
msgstr "6200:I only had Kozupii's word for that.[%p]"

msgid "6300:こずぴぃが嘘をついているのかどうか判断できない。[%p]"
msgstr "6300:And I couldn't tell if Kozupii was lying or not.[%p]"

msgid "6400:ゾワリと、全身の産毛が逆立つような感覚。[%p]"
msgstr "6400:I could feel the hairs on my body began to stand up on end.[%p]"

msgid "6500:やっぱり、僕っていう世界はあまりにも虚ろだ。[%p]"
msgstr "6500:My world was just an empty, desolate place.[%p]"

msgid "6600:信じるべき拠り所がない。[linebreak]なにもかもが嘘に見えてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "6600:I had nothing to believe in. Everything seemed like a lie.[%p]"

msgid "6700:[name]梢[line]「そーれーは、被害妄想なのら」[%p]"
msgstr "6700:[name]梢[line]That's called a paranoid delusion, nora.[%p]"

msgid "6800:こずぴぃが、すぐ後ろに立っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "6800:Kozupii was standing right behind me.[%p]"

msgid "6900:心の声は相変わらず脳天気。[%p]"
msgstr "6900:Her internal voice was as happy as ever.[%p]"

msgid "7000:両手で、凶悪そうなディソードを抱え。[linebreak]上目遣いで僕を見ている。[%p]"
msgstr "7000:She was carrying her wicked-looking Di-Sword in her hands, and looking up at me innocently.[%p]"

msgid "7100:僕はそんな彼女から目をそらした。[%p]"
msgstr "7100:I looked away.[%p]"

msgid "7200:君は……僕の味方？[linebreak]それとも、敵？[linebreak]どっちなの？[%p]"
msgstr "7200:Are you... on my side? Or my enemy? Which?[%p]"

msgid "7300:[name]梢[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "7300:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "7400:君は、僕を殺しに来たの？[%p]"
msgstr "7400:Did you come to kill me?[%p]"

msgid "7500:[name]梢[line]「こずぴぃは、ただ――」[%p]"
msgstr "7500:[name]梢[line]Kozupii just...[%p]"

msgid "7600:ただ……？[%p]"
msgstr "7600:Just?[%p]"

msgid "7700:[name]梢[line]「あー！」[%p]"
msgstr "7700:[name]梢[line]Oh![%p]"

msgid "7800:いきなりこずぴぃは奇声をあげた。[%p]"
msgstr "7800:Kozupii suddenly let out a weird shout.[%p]"

msgid "7900:びっくりして顔を上げると、彼女は僕を見ていなくて、あらぬ方へ手を振っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "7900:I looked up in surprise to see that she wasn't looking at me, but waving her hand off in a random direction.[%p]"

msgid "8000:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃんみっけー」[%p]"
msgstr "8000:[name]梢[line]I found Sena![%p]"

msgid "8100:セナ……しゃん？[linebreak]まさか……[%p]"
msgstr "8100:Did she say... Sena? Don't tell me.[%p]"

msgid "8200:こずぴぃの視線を追っていくと、そこにいたのは案の定――[%p]"
msgstr "8200:I followed where she was looking, and sure enough...[%p]"

msgid "8300:[name]セナ[line]「……梢か」[%p]"
msgstr "8300:[name]セナ[line]Oh, is that you, Kozue?[%p]"

msgid "8400:不機嫌きわまりないと言った表情で、ディソードを担いだ蒼井セナが歩いてくるところだった。[%p]"
msgstr "8400:Sena Aoi was walking towards us, holding a Di-Sword and looking like she was in an extremely bad mood.[%p]"

msgid "8500:僕はついつい身構えてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "8500:I tensed up and got ready to run.[%p]"

msgid "8600:なぜセナがここで現れる？[linebreak]これも偶然？[linebreak]それとも……計算された罠？[%p]"
msgstr "8600:What was Sena doing here? Was this another coincidence? Or... a carefully planned trap?[%p]"

msgid "8700:２人は知り合いなの？[linebreak]だとしたらこずぴぃが呼び込んだ？[linebreak]２人がかりで僕を殺すため？[%p]"
msgstr "8700:Did the two of them know each other? If so, had Kozupii called her? Maybe so the two of them could kill me together?[%p]"

msgid "8800:[name]梢[line]「だーからー、それは被害妄想だよー」[%p]"
msgstr "8800:[name]梢[line]I told you, that's a paranoid delusion![%p]"

msgid "8900:だって、なにを信じていいのか……。[%p]"
msgstr "8900:But... I don't know what to believe in.[%p]"

msgid "9000:セナはこれまでにも何度か遭遇してるけど、僕を攻撃しようとはしなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "9000:I'd met Sena several times, and she'd never tried to hurt me.[%p]"

msgid "9100:だからって、僕の味方だとは限らない。[linebreak]それに……怖いし。[%p]"
msgstr "9100:But that didn't mean she wasn't my enemy. And... she was scary.[%p]"

msgid "9200:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃんは怖くなーいよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9200:[name]梢[line]Sena's not scary![%p]"

msgid "9300:[name]拓巳[line]「ちょ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "9300:[name]拓巳[line]Hey![%p]"

msgid "9400:こずぴぃ、そういう余計なこと言わないでくれよぅ！[%p]"
msgstr "9400:Kozupii, don't say that where she can hear it![%p]"

msgid "9500:[name]セナ[line]「怖い？\u3000なんのことだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "9500:[name]セナ[line]Scary? What are you talking about?[%p]"

msgid "9600:案の定、セナにもこずぴぃの“心の声”が聞こえるらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "9600:Just like I thought, Sena could hear Kozupii's “voice,” too.[%p]"

msgid "9700:[name]拓巳[line]「な、なな、なんでも、ない、です……」[%p]"
msgstr "9700:[name]拓巳[line]N-N-Nothing...[%p]"

msgid "9800:焦る僕を尻目に、こずぴぃはやけに嬉しそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "9800:I was freaking out, but Kozupii looked really happy.[%p]"

msgid "9900:うつむきがちながらも、セナの服の裾をそっと握りしめはにかんでいる。[%p]"
msgstr "9900:She was still staring at the ground, but she was smiling as she tugged at the hem of Sena's shirt.[%p]"

msgid "10000:あまりにも２人の組み合わせが微笑ましくて、自分が緊張しているのがバカみたいに思えてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "10000:The sight of the two of them was so... heartwarming... that I started to feel stupid for being nervous.[%p]"

msgid "10100:２人は、まるで姉妹だ。気が強くてしっかり者の姉と、姉のことが大好きなおとなしい妹。[%p]"
msgstr "10100:They were like sisters. The strong-willed big sister, and the timid little sister who looked up to her more than anyone else in the world.[%p]"

msgid "10200:しかも２人とも貧乳とかもうね、ＧＪすぎる――[%p]"
msgstr "10200:And they both had flat chests! GJ![%p]"

msgid "10300:って、ダメだダメだ、自重しろ！\u3000こずぴぃにまた心を読まれる！[linebreak]それに、油断すると命取りになるぞ……。[%p]"
msgstr "10300:No, wait! Wait! Don't think that! Kozupii will hear you again! And... if you're not careful, you could easily die here.[%p]"

msgid "10400:２人はいったいどういう繋がりなんだろう。学校で知り合ったのかな？\u3000でも学年が違うし……。[%p]"
msgstr "10400:What was the deal with these two? Did they know each other from school? But they were in different grades.[%p]"

msgid "10500:剣を持つ者同士の繋がりみたいなものがあるのか。２人とも『将軍』の手下なのか。[%p]"
msgstr "10500:Maybe they were both connected by the fact that they had the swords? Or maybe they both worked for Shogun.[%p]"

msgid "10600:僕はいつでも逃げ出せるように、猫足立ちの姿勢を取った。[%p]"
msgstr "10600:I got into a “cat's paw” stance so I could run at any moment.[%p]"

msgid "10700:具体的には、足のかかとを上げて立つこと。こうすることで猫のように素早く動き出すことができる……らしい。昔、マンガで読んだ。[%p]"
msgstr "10700:Specifically, I stood up on my tiptoes. Supposedly, this made it so you could run really fast... like a cat, I guess. I'd read about it in a manga once.[%p]"

msgid "10800:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃんはねー、こずぴぃが東京に来てから最初のお友達なのらー。ね？\u3000ね？」[%p]"
msgstr "10800:[name]梢[line]Sena is the first friend Kozupii made since coming to Tokyo, nora. Right? Right?[%p]"

msgid "10900:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "10900:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "11000:それには答えず、セナは僕をギロリとにらみつけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "11000:Sena didn't answer. Instead, she just glared at me.[%p]"

msgid "11100:持っている剣で襲いかかってこられるのかと思ったけど、なにもなかった。[linebreak]怖いって言ったことを特に怒る様子もない。[%p]"
msgstr "11100:I thought she might attack me with the sword in her hand, but she didn't do anything. She didn't seem really upset that I called her scary, either.[%p]"

msgid "11200:[name]セナ[line]「梢、どうしてこいつと？」[%p]"
msgstr "11200:[name]セナ[line]Kozue, what are you doing with him?[%p]"

msgid "11300:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんは、クラスメイトでーす」[%p]"
msgstr "11300:[name]梢[line]Takumi's my classmate![%p]"

msgid "11400:た、拓巳しゃん……って……[%p]"
msgstr "11400:She sounded really excited about it.[%p]"

msgid "11500:[name]梢[line]「ほいでね、拓巳しゃんはこずぴぃの剣が見えるんだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "11500:[name]梢[line]And! And! He can see Kozupii's sword, too![%p]"

msgid "11600:[name]セナ[line]「それは知っている。こいつもギガロマニアックスだ」[%p]"
msgstr "11600:[name]セナ[line]I know that. He's a Gigalomaniac.[%p]"

msgid "11700:ギガロ……なんだって？[%p]"
msgstr "11700:A Gigalo... what?[%p]"

msgid "11800:[name]梢[line]「ギガロマニアックス」[%p]"
msgstr "11800:[name]梢[line]A Gigalomaniac.[%p]"

msgid "11900:[name]梢[line]「ディソードが見える人のことー」[%p]"
msgstr "11900:[name]梢[line]Somebody who can see a Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "12000:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんもそうだよ」[%p]"
msgstr "12000:[name]梢[line]That includes you![%p]"

msgid "12100:ギガロマニアックス……。[%p]"
msgstr "12100:Gigalomaniac...[%p]"

msgid "12200:その名称を決めたのは、どこの誰？[%p]"
msgstr "12200:Who the hell had picked that name?[%p]"

msgid "12300:呼び名があるっていうことは、その力は珍しくないものなの？[%p]"
msgstr "12300:And if it had a name, did that mean it was more common than I thought it was?[%p]"

msgid "12400:[name]梢[line]「あ、セナしゃんは『ガルガリ君』買いーにいくとこなんですねー？」[%p]"
msgstr "12400:[name]梢[line]Oh, Sena's about to go buy a Garugari-kun bar![%p]"

msgid "12500:[name]セナ[line]「う、そ、それは……」[%p]"
msgstr "12500:[name]セナ[line]Um, well...[%p]"

msgid "12600:どうやらこずぴぃはセナの心を読んだらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "12600:Evidently Kozupii had read Sena's mind.[%p]"

msgid "12700:そう言えばセナは、前もガルガリ君を食べていた。[%p]"
msgstr "12700:Come to think of it, Sena had been eating a Garugari-kun bar the last time we met, too.[%p]"

msgid "12800:もうすぐ冬。だいぶ寒くなってきたっていうのに、よく外でアイスなんて食べられるもんだ。[linebreak]よっぽど好きなのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "12800:It was almost winter. With the weather this cold, I couldn't understand why anybody would want to eat popsicles. She must really like them.[%p]"

msgid "12900:[name]梢[line]「ほいじゃ、みんなで一緒に行きましょー」[%p]"
msgstr "12900:[name]梢[line]Okay, let's all get one together![%p]"

msgid "13000:こずぴぃは心の声でそう宣言すると、セナにじゃれつくように手を引っ張って歩き出した。[%p]"
msgstr "13000:I heard Kozupii's voice speak in my head as she playfully grabbed Sena's hand and started to walk.[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんもはーやく」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]梢[line]Takumi, you too![%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、え、いや、僕は……」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]拓巳[line]Oh, um, I...[%p]"

msgid "13300:辞退してさっさと帰ろうとしたけど、[%p]"
msgstr "13300:I turned to leave, but...[%p]"

msgid "13400:[name]梢[line]「……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "13400:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "13500:途端にこずぴぃが涙目になった。潤んだ眼差しで僕に無言で訴えかけてくる。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:Suddenly Kozupii's eyes were filled with tears. She silently pleaded to me with her wet eyes.[%p]"

msgid "13600:その隣では、セナが今にも噛みつきそうなくらいに睨んでくるし。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:Next to her, Sena was looking like she was ready to bite my head off.[%p]"

msgid "13700:[name]セナ[line]「……ついてこい」[%p]"
msgstr "13700:[name]セナ[line]Come with us.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]セナ[line]「お前にもおごってやる」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]セナ[line]My treat.[%p]"

msgid "13900:どうやらセナも、こずぴぃの涙目攻撃には弱いらしかった。渋々といった感じで僕を促し、交番のすぐ裏にあるコンビニへ向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "13900:From the look of it, Sena was weak to Kozupii's teary eyes attack, too. She motioned to me, reluctantly, and we started heading toward the convenience store right behind the police box.[%p]"

msgid "14000:ガルガリ君を１本ずつ買い、交番前の手すりに腰かけて２人はかじり始める。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:We each bought a Garugari-kun, and the two of them sat down on the railings in front of the police box and began to nibble on their popsicles.[%p]"

msgid "14100:こずぴぃはやっぱり嬉しそうだ。一方のセナは澄ました顔。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:Kozupii looked really happy. Sena looked... straightfaced.[%p]"

msgid "14200:僕は気が気じゃなかった。[linebreak]目の前の交番には警官がいる。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I was on the verge of passing out from fear. There was a cop right in front of the police box.[%p]"

msgid "14300:なのに、銃刀法を現在進行形で違反中の２人は、まったくそれに注意を払う素振りも見せない。[%p]"
msgstr "14300:But the girls didn't seem concerned in the slightest that they were violating Japan's laws against deadly weapons right in front of his face.[%p]"

msgid "14400:警官も警官だ。[linebreak]明らかに僕らのことが見えているはずなのに、逮捕どころか、注意しに出てくることすらなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "14400:And what was the cop's problem? I could see the two giant swords right in front of his face just fine, but instead of arresting them, he was ignoring them.[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]梢[line]「食べないのー？」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]梢[line]You're not going to eat yours?[%p]"

msgid "14600:こずぴぃに指摘されて、手に持っているガルガリ君を仕方なくかじる。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Since Kozupii was watching, I had no choice but to start nibbling on my Garugari-kun.[%p]"

msgid "14700:周囲の視線が気になる。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:I was intensely focused on where the people around us were looking.[%p]"

msgid "14800:セナとこずぴぃはかわいい。こんなかわいい“貧乳姉妹”と僕みたいなキモオタが３人一緒にいて、しかも３人とも寒空の下でガルガリ君を食べているのは、あまりにシュールすぎて目立ってしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "14800:Sena and Kozupii were cute. The sight of two cute “flat-chested sisters” and a creepy otaku like me, standing out in the winter cold and eating popsicles, was so surreal that we were sure to stand out.[%p]"

msgid "14900:自意識過剰かな？[%p]"
msgstr "14900:Or was I being paranoid after all?[%p]"

msgid "15000:クスクスというバカにしたような笑い声がずっと聞こえている。幻聴？\u3000こずぴぃが笑ってるだけ？[%p]"
msgstr "15000:I could still hear the chuckles of my classmates. Was I hearing things? Was I imagining them?[%p]"

msgid "15100:目立ちたくない。[linebreak]見られたくない。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:I didn't want to stand out. I didn't want to be seen.[%p]"

msgid "15200:他人の視線に対する恐怖。[linebreak]帽子でも被ってくればよかった……。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:I was scared of other people's gazes. I should've worn a hat.[%p]"

msgid "15300:とにかく一刻も早くこの場から立ち去りたい。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:I wanted to get out of here as soon as possible.[%p]"

msgid "15400:そのために必死でガルガリ君を食べ進めるうちに、身体が冷えてきた。後で絶対下痢になるぞこれ……。２人は寒くないんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:I decided the fastest way to do this was to chow down on my popsicle. As I did, though, my body started to freeze. This was definitely going to give me diarrhea later... And weren't the two of them cold?[%p]"

msgid "15500:[name]セナ[line]「で、梢。なぜこいつと一緒なんだ？」[%p]"
msgstr "15500:[name]セナ[line]So, Kozue. What are you doing with this guy?[%p]"

msgid "15600:[name]梢[line]「こいつーじゃなくて拓巳しゃんでーすよ」[%p]"
msgstr "15600:[name]梢[line]He has a name, you know! Takumi![%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃんが悪い人にいじめられてて、倒れてたのら。だからこずぴぃが介抱してあげたの」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]梢[line]Takumi was being bullied by bad people, and he got hurt. So Kozupii nursed him back to health![%p]"

msgid "15800:介抱……されたかな？[%p]"
msgstr "15800:Did she nurse me?[%p]"

msgid "15900:[name]セナ[line]「ディソードを使ったのか」[%p]"
msgstr "15900:[name]セナ[line]You used the Di-Sword?[%p]"

msgid "16000:[name]梢[line]「殺したかったぁ。ドカバキィッて！」[%p]"
msgstr "16000:[name]梢[line]I wanted to kill them! Ker-SLAM![%p]"

msgid "16100:こずぴぃは身振り手振りで表現しようとしたらしい。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Kozupii tried to mimic the motion of killing someone with her hands.[%p]"

msgid "16200:でも左手には巨大なディソードを持っていたから、もう片方の手を振り回す。[%p]"
msgstr "16200:But since one hand was holding the huge Di-Sword, she had to do it with the other.[%p]"

msgid "16300:でもそっちには当然ながらガルガリ君が握られていたわけで。[%p]"
msgstr "16300:And of course, the other hand held her Garugari-kun.[%p]"

msgid "16400:[name]梢[line]「……っ！」[%p]"
msgstr "16400:[name]梢[line]...![%p]"

msgid "16500:まだ一口しかかじっていなかったこずぴぃのガルガリ君が、キレイな弧を描いて飛んでいった。そして道路の上に落ち、砕けた。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:Her popsicle, which she hadn't taken a single bite of, flew out of her hand in a perfect arc. Then it landed on the ground and shattered.[%p]"

msgid "16600:[name]梢[line]「……っ、……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "16600:[name]梢[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16700:こずぴぃは泣きそうになって、その残骸となったアイスを見つめている。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:Kozupii looked at the remains of her popsicle with tears in her eyes.[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]セナ[line]「……迂闊なマネは避けろと言っただろう」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]セナ[line]I told you to be careful.[%p]"

msgid "16900:[name]梢[line]「うう、ごめーんなさい……。もったいないないオバケが出ちゃう……」[%p]"
msgstr "16900:[name]梢[line]Waah... I'm sorry. The Don't-Waste-Food Monster's gonna get me.[%p]"

msgid "17000:[name]セナ[line]「アイスのことじゃない。ディソードのことだ」[%p]"
msgstr "17000:[name]セナ[line]I don't mean the popsicle. I mean the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "17100:セナがこずぴぃに、自分の食べかけのガルガリ君を渡した。どうやらこずぴぃにあげるらしい。受け取ったこずぴぃは泣きながらはにかんで、ペコペコと頭を下げた。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Sena handed Kozupii her half-eaten Garugari-kun. Evidently, she was giving it to her. Kozupii smiled through her tears and bobbed her head in thanks.[%p]"

msgid "17200:セナにもこんな優しいところがあるなんて。意外だ。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:I didn't realize that Sena could be so nice. That was surprising.[%p]"

msgid "17300:[name]梢[line]「でもでも、悪い人には罰ゲームをするのがあったーり前だよぉ」[%p]"
msgstr "17300:[name]梢[line]It was so surprising...[%p]"

msgid "17400:あの連中を血祭りに上げたのは……誰なんだろう。[linebreak]こずぴぃなんだろうか。[linebreak]それとも……僕？[%p]"
msgstr "17400:Who was it who'd hurt those thugs so badly? Was it Kozupii? Or... was it me?[%p]"

msgid "17500:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃん拓巳しゃん」[%p]"
msgstr "17500:[name]梢[line]Takumi! Takumi![%p]"

msgid "17600:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃんはねぇ、すごーくなんでも知ってるんだよー」[%p]"
msgstr "17600:[name]梢[line]Sena knows a whole lot of things![%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]梢[line]「ディソードっていう名前も、セナしゃんに教えてもらったのら」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]梢[line]She was the one who told me the name Di-Sword![%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]梢[line]「あとあと、リアルブータ？\u3000あれれ？\u3000ブタ？\u3000ブッダ？」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]梢[line]And... Real Butts? Huh? Butts? Buddha?[%p]"

msgid "17900:[name]セナ[line]「……リアルブート」[%p]"
msgstr "17900:[name]セナ[line]Real boot.[%p]"

msgid "18000:[name]梢[line]「あ、そそ」[%p]"
msgstr "18000:[name]梢[line]Oh, right.[%p]"

msgid "18100:なんだそれ。そんな言葉、初めて聞いたぞ……。[linebreak]さっきの、ギガロなんとかもそうだし。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:What was that? I'd never heard that word before. Or that Gigalowhatsit word, for that matter.[%p]"

msgid "18200:[name]梢[line]「リアルブートしてない剣は、誰にも見えなかったはずなのにね、セナしゃんにだけ見えてたの！」[%p]"
msgstr "18200:[name]梢[line]Nobody else could see my sword when it wasn't real-booted, but Sena could![%p]"

msgid "18300:[name]梢[line]「ディソードが見える人に会ったの、セナしゃんがはーじめてだったんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "18300:[name]梢[line]Sena was the first person I met who could see a Di-Sword![%p]"

msgid "18400:[name]梢[line]「そのときはほひゃーって思って、なんで見えるんですかーって聞いちゃった」[%p]"
msgstr "18400:[name]梢[line]When I realized, I went ‘Hohyaaah!’ And then I asked how she could see it![%p]"

msgid "18500:[name]梢[line]「ギガロマニアックスだからなんだって」[%p]"
msgstr "18500:[name]梢[line]She said it's because she's a Gigalomaniac.[%p]"

msgid "18600:[name]拓巳[line]「ギガロマニアックスって……なんなの？」[%p]"
msgstr "18600:[name]拓巳[line]What's a Gigalomaniac?[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]梢[line]「さっき言ったのらー」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]梢[line]I just told you, nora![%p]"

msgid "18800:[name]梢[line]「剣が見える人だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "18800:[name]梢[line]It's somebody who can see the sword.[%p]"

msgid "18900:いや、もっと詳しく、えっと、原理とか……[%p]"
msgstr "18900:No, I meant more specifically, like... how does it work?[%p]"

msgid "19000:[name]セナ[line]「“[color index="A0FF0000"]ディラックの海[color index="800000"]”に干渉できる力を持つ者」[%p]"
msgstr "19000:[name]セナ[line]Someone with the power to exert influence on the [color index="A0FF0000"]Dirac Sea[color index="800000"].[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]セナ[line]「それが、ギガロマニアックスだ」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]セナ[line]That's what a Gigalomaniac is.[%p]"

msgid "19200:代わりにセナが答えてくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "19200:Sena answered instead.[%p]"

msgid "19300:[name]梢[line]「？？？」[%p]"
msgstr "19300:[name]梢[line]???[%p]"

msgid "19400:[name]拓巳[line]「ディラックの海……？」[%p]"
msgstr "19400:[name]拓巳[line]The Dirac Sea?[%p]"

msgid "19500:首を傾げる僕に、セナは蔑むような一瞥をくれた。[%p]"
msgstr "19500:Sena glanced at me contemptuously when I didn't recognize the term.[%p]"

msgid "19600:な、なんだよ、その目は……。[linebreak]こう見えても僕は頭がいいんだぞ。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:W-Why are you looking at me like that? I'm actually pretty smart, you know...[%p]"

msgid "19700:確か“ディラックの海”って、量子力学の概念かなにかだったような気がする。[%p]"
msgstr "19700:I vaguely remembered the Dirac Sea being some concept in quantum physics.[%p]"

msgid "19800:[name]拓巳[line]「負の、エ、エネルギーでいっぱいに満たされた……観測不能の境界面……とか、だっけ？」[%p]"
msgstr "19800:[name]拓巳[line]I-It's like... an unobservable boundary plane... filled with negative energy, or something?[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]セナ[line]「大ざっぱに言えばそんなようなものだ」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]セナ[line]That's the general idea.[%p]"

msgid "20000:[name]セナ[line]「そしてそこに干渉するための端末が、ディソード。ディラックの海に突っ込んだパイプの先端と考えればいい」[%p]"
msgstr "20000:[name]セナ[line]And the Di-Sword is a terminal that allows you to interact with it. Think of it like a pipe with its other end stuck into the Dirac Sea.[%p]"

msgid "20100:[name]セナ[line]「ディラックの海と繋がっているから、ディソードも[color index="A0FF0000"]負の物質[color index="800000"]で構成されている。無限に崩壊している存在なんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "20100:[name]セナ[line]Since the sword is connected to the Dirac Sea, it's also composed of [color index="A0FF0000"]negative matter[color index="800000"]. It's constantly, infinitely collapsing.[%p]"

msgid "20200:[name]セナ[line]「だから普段は普通の人間には触れることも見ることもできない、妄想のようなものでしかない」[%p]"
msgstr "20200:[name]セナ[line]That's why normal people can't see or interact with it. It's essentially nothing more than a delusion.[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]セナ[line]「このディソードこそ、あらゆるリアルブートのためのショートカット的役割を果たす」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]セナ[line]The Di-Sword serves as a shortcut for all kinds of real boots.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]セナ[line]「ディソードとディラックの海とのチャネルを大きくすることで――」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]セナ[line]By expanding the channel between the Dirac Sea and the Di-Sword...[%p]"

msgid "20500:[name]セナ[line]「ディラック方程式の[color index="A0FF0000"]空孔理論[color index="800000"]によって[color index="A0FE0000"]対生成[color index="800000"]が起き、[color index="A0FD0000"]粒子[color index="800000"]と反粒子を作り出せる」[%p]"
msgstr "20500:[name]セナ[line]The Dirac equation's [color index="A0FF0000"]hole theory[color index="800000"] causes [color index="A0FE0000"]pair production[color index="800000"], [color index="A0FD0000"]generating particles[color index="800000"] and anti-particles.[%p]"

msgid "20600:[name]セナ[line]「この粒子が、ギガロマニアックスが生み出す妄想、世界にとってのエラー」[%p]"
msgstr "20600:[name]セナ[line]These particles are the delusions generated by Gigalomaniacs. From our universe's perspective, they're best thought of as “errors.”[%p]"

msgid "20700:[name]セナ[line]「そのエラーを現実とするには、作り出した粒子を他人のデッドスポットに送り込めばいい」[%p]"
msgstr "20700:[name]セナ[line]If you want to make these errors real, you send the generated particles into other people's dead spots.[%p]"

msgid "20800:[name]セナ[line]「粒子は即座に電気信号に変換され、周囲の人間に共通の認識――現実として成立する」[%p]"
msgstr "20800:[name]セナ[line]The particles are immediately converted into electrical signals, and generate a shared awareness in the people around you, thus becoming real.[%p]"

msgid "20900:[name]セナ[line]「逆に消したいときは、粒子を送り込んだデッドスポットに、今度は反粒子を送り込み、対消滅してやればいい」[%p]"
msgstr "20900:[name]セナ[line]And if you want to get rid of them, you simply do the opposite. You send antiparticles into the dead spots to cause pair annihilation.[%p]"

msgid "21000:[name]梢[line]「？？？」[%p]"
msgstr "21000:[name]梢[line]???[%p]"

msgid "21100:そういえば、前にもセナは言っていたっけ。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Come to think of it, Sena had said something similar before.[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]セナ[line]「世界の仕組みは、３つの数字ですべて説明できる。[linebreak]０と１、そして－１」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]セナ[line]There are three numbers that can explain the entire way the world functions. Zero. One. And minus one.[%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]セナ[line]「ディソードはその－１を生み出すためのショートカットになる」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]セナ[line]The Di-Sword is a shortcut to creating that minus one.[%p]"

msgid "21400:なんだか頭がこんがらがっちゃいそうだよ……。[%p]"
msgstr "21400:This was starting to make my head hurt.[%p]"

msgid "21500:[name]拓巳[line]「周囲の人間に共通の認識となると、[linebreak]妄想が現実になるって……どういうこと？」[%p]"
msgstr "21500:[name]拓巳[line]So, you're saying that if the people around you all recognize your delusion as real in the same way, then it becomes real?[%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]セナ[line]「例えばお前が今手にしている、ガルガリ君。お前にはどう見える」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]セナ[line]Let's take the Garugari-kun you're holding as an example. What does it look like to you?[%p]"

msgid "21700:[name]拓巳[line]「え、どうって……水色をしたアイス……」[%p]"
msgstr "21700:[name]拓巳[line]Um... it looks like a blue popsicle.[%p]"

msgid "21800:[name]セナ[line]「その水色のアイスは本当に“現実”だと証明できるか？」[%p]"
msgstr "21800:[name]セナ[line]Can you prove that this blue popsicle actually exists?[%p]"

msgid "21900:ガルガリ君はガルガリ君じゃないか。目で見ればすぐ分かるし、食べれば冷たい。そんなの分かりきったことだと思うけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "21900:What else could it be but a Garugari-kun, though? You could recognize it instantly by its distinctive color. And if you ate it, it would feel cold. This should be common sense, but...[%p]"

msgid "22000:[name]セナ[line]「人は目で見たものを脳が認識して初めて“それが水色のアイス”と理解できる」[%p]"
msgstr "22000:[name]セナ[line]A human being can only understand that object you're holding as a “blue popsicle” after their brain becomes aware of what it sees.[%p]"

msgid "22100:[name]セナ[line]「でも、脳が本人の意識しないままに“ウソをついている”可能性だってあるんだぞ」[%p]"
msgstr "22100:[name]セナ[line]But there's also the possibility that your brain is lying to you, and you aren't conscious of it.[%p]"

msgid "22200:[name]セナ[line]「“脳が生み出した、自分ひとりだけがそう思い込んでいる妄想”かもしれないんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "22200:[name]セナ[line]It's possible that what you're seeing is, in fact a delusion, generated by your brain.[%p]"

msgid "22300:[name]拓巳[line]「じゃ、じゃあ、どうやって、現実だって、しょ、証明、するの？」[%p]"
msgstr "22300:[name]拓巳[line]T-Then... how do you prove something's real?[%p]"

msgid "22400:[name]セナ[line]「他の人も、お前の持っているものが水色のアイスであると観測すれば、それは２人以上の人間の共通の認識となる」[%p]"
msgstr "22400:[name]セナ[line]If others observe that the item you're holding is a blue popsicle, then you've created a shared awareness between at least two people.[%p]"

msgid "22500:[name]セナ[line]「お前ひとりだけの妄想じゃなくなるんだ」[%p]"
msgstr "22500:[name]セナ[line]It's no longer just your delusion.[%p]"

msgid "22600:[name]セナ[line]「妄想を現実にするときには、それを逆説的に捉えればいい」[%p]"
msgstr "22600:[name]セナ[line]Turn the process around and you can make a delusion into reality.[%p]"

msgid "22700:つまり、自分１人だけの妄想――ディソードによって作り出した粒子を、周囲の人間に強制的に“見せる”ことで、妄想は現実となる……っていうことか。[%p]"
msgstr "22700:So, in other words, you could create a delusion in your own mind, and using the particles created by the Di-Sword, force the other people around you to “see” it, thereby making it real.[%p]"

msgid "22800:で、その力は、僕にもある……のか？[%p]"
msgstr "22800:And... I had this power too?[%p]"

msgid "22900:[name]梢[line]「ふみゅー。こずぴぃ、さっぱり〜」[%p]"
msgstr "22900:[name]梢[line]Fumyuu... Kozupii didn't understand that at all![%p]"

msgid "23000:[name]梢[line]「とにかく、この剣は普通の人には見えないのー」[%p]"
msgstr "23000:[name]梢[line]Anyway, normal people can't see this sword![%p]"

msgid "23100:こずぴぃはガルガリ君をセナに返すと、とてとてと道路へと走り出た。[%p]"
msgstr "23100:Kozupii gave the Garugari-kun back to Sena, and suddenly ran out toward the street.[%p]"

msgid "23200:道を歩いている人たちを前にして、なにを思ったか、いきなり持っているディソードを豪快に振り回す。[%p]"
msgstr "23200:For some reason, she began to swing the Di-Sword at the people around her.[%p]"

msgid "23300:[name]拓巳[line]「やめっ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "23300:[name]拓巳[line]No...![%p]"

msgid "23400:僕は目を覆った。[%p]"
msgstr "23400:I covered my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "23500:ついに本性を現した――！[linebreak]実はとんでもない殺人鬼だったんだ！[%p]"
msgstr "23500:She'd finally revealed her true nature! Kozupii was actually an insane killer![%p]"

msgid "23600:今頃道路が血の海になってる。[%p]"
msgstr "23600:The street must be covered in blood right now.[%p]"

msgid "23700:あの巨大な剣で斬りつけられたら、胴体ごとまっぷたつだ。[%p]"
msgstr "23700:One thwack with that gigantic sword and you'd be sliced in two.[%p]"

msgid "23800:こずぴぃは現行犯逮捕だ。なにしろ目の前は交番。警官がしっかり目撃してる。[%p]"
msgstr "23800:Kozupii would be arrested on the spot. We were right in front of a police box, after all. The cops would've seen the whole thing.[%p]"

msgid "23900:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃん、そんなことにはなってなーいよ？」[%p]"
msgstr "23900:[name]梢[line]Takumi, that didn't happen at all![%p]"

msgid "24000:……どうして、こんなに静かなんだろう。[linebreak]白昼堂々、渋谷のど真ん中で人が剣でぶった斬られたのに。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:Why was it so quiet? She'd just killed people with a sword, in broad daylight, in the middle of Shibuya.[%p]"

msgid "24100:誰も悲鳴をあげない。[linebreak]警官の怒声も聞こえない。[%p]"
msgstr "24100:But nobody was screaming. I couldn't hear any cops shouting, either.[%p]"

msgid "24200:目を、ゆっくりと開いてみた。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:I slowly opened my eyes.[%p]"

msgid "24300:……なにも起きていなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "24300:Nothing had happened.[%p]"

msgid "24400:こずぴぃはなおも――少し恥ずかしそうに――巨大な剣を振り回している。[%p]"
msgstr "24400:Kozupii was still swinging around the sword... though now she looked a little embarrassed.[%p]"

msgid "24500:明らかに通行人や柵、地面にも剣はぶつかってるはずなのに、なにも起きない。なにも斬れない。[%p]"
msgstr "24500:It was colliding with other people, with railings, with the ground... but nothing happened. It wasn't cutting anything.[%p]"

msgid "24600:それどころか、剣が――[linebreak]ものを、すり抜けている。[linebreak]まるで、それらが幻であるかのように。[%p]"
msgstr "24600:In fact, the sword... was going right through it all. As if everything around it was just an illusion.[%p]"

msgid "24700:いや、違う。逆だ。[linebreak]剣の方に実体がないんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:No, that wasn't right. It was the other way around. The sword was what didn't exist.[%p]"

msgid "24800:周囲を歩く人たちはまったく動じてない。[linebreak]この剣が見えていない。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:The people around her weren't reacting at all. They couldn't see it.[%p]"

msgid "24900:[name]梢[line]「ピンポンピンポーン」[%p]"
msgstr "24900:[name]梢[line]Ding-ding-ding-ding![%p]"

msgid "25000:[name]梢[line]「ディソードは、妄想の剣なのだ」[%p]"
msgstr "25000:[name]梢[line]The Di-Sword is made out of delusions![%p]"

msgid "25100:そう言えば、以前あやせもそんなようなことを言ってた。剣は力を持つ人の目にしか映らない、って。[%p]"
msgstr "25100:Ayase had said something similar once, actually. She'd said that only those with the power could see the sword.[%p]"

msgid "25200:僕の隣でセナが面倒くさそうにため息をつき、ガルガリ君をかじった。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:Next to me, Sena sighed in annoyance and nibbled on her Garugari-kun.[%p]"

msgid "25300:[name]セナ[line]「あのディソードは今は梢の作ったエラーでしかない」[%p]"
msgstr "25300:[name]セナ[line]Right now, that Di-Sword is nothing more than an error that Kozue created.[%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]セナ[line]「周囲共通認識はまだ成立していない」[%p]"
msgstr "25400:[name]セナ[line]She hasn't created any shared awareness yet.[%p]"

msgid "25500:[name]梢[line]「リアルブートしたら、みんなに見えるようになるのでーす」[%p]"
msgstr "25500:[name]梢[line]If I real boot it, everybody will be able to see it![%p]"

msgid "25600:リアルブート……。[%p]"
msgstr "25600:Real booting...[%p]"

msgid "25700:それが“周囲の人間のデッドスポットに粒子を送り込む”行為なのか。[linebreak]デッドスポットっていうのがなんなのかは分からないけど。[%p]"
msgstr "25700:That would be when you send particles into other people's dead spots, right? Not that I was sure what a dead spot was.[%p]"

msgid "25800:[name]梢[line]「ズシャァッてしたりドガァッてできるようにもなるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "25800:[name]梢[line]Then you can go swaash! And ker-thwack![%p]"

msgid "25900:擬音じゃなくてもっと分かりやすく説明してくれ……。[%p]"
msgstr "25900:I'd like it a lot more if she used words instead of sound effects.[%p]"

msgid "26000:でも、なんとなくニュアンスは伝わった。[linebreak]ズシャァッは、たぶん……剣で斬ること。[linebreak]ドガァッは、殴ること？[%p]"
msgstr "26000:But I kind of got the basic idea. Swaash was probably... swinging the sword? And ker-thwack would be... hitting with it?[%p]"

msgid "26100:なにを、斬ったり殴ったり……しているんだろう。[linebreak]そんなおっかないことを、こずぴぃはやってるの？[%p]"
msgstr "26100:What was she swinging at, and what was she hitting? Was Kozupii really doing something so scary?[%p]"

msgid "26200:僕も……[linebreak]僕にもそんな力があるのかな……[%p]"
msgstr "26200:And did I... Did I have that power, too?[%p]"

msgid "26300:いや……僕は特別じゃない。[linebreak]ギガロマニアックスなんかじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "26300:No... I wasn't special. I'm not a Gigalomaniac, whatever that is.[%p]"

msgid "26400:だって、結局、ディソードを手に入れることはできなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "26400:That's why I couldn't get my Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "26500:[name]梢[line]「剣は見えたーよね？」[%p]"
msgstr "26500:[name]梢[line]But you saw it, right?[%p]"

msgid "26600:[name]梢[line]「だからそのうち拓巳しゃんも持てるのー」[%p]"
msgstr "26600:[name]梢[line]So eventually, you'll get one.[%p]"

msgid "26700:無理だよ……。[linebreak]あのＯ－ＦＲＯＮＴのときだって、無理だった。[linebreak]剣は見えてたけど、つかむ方法が分からなくて……[%p]"
msgstr "26700:I can't... Even when all that stuff was happening at O-FRONT, I couldn't get it. I could see it, but I didn't know how to grab it.[%p]"

msgid "26800:[name]梢[line]「えーと、どうやって手に入れるかって言うとー」[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[name]梢[line]Um... as for how you get it...[%p]"

msgid "26900:こずぴぃが指をくわえてセナを見る。[linebreak]セナはまたため息をついた。[%p]"
msgstr "26900:Kozupii looked at Sena expectantly. Sena sighed again.[%p]"

msgid "27000:[name]セナ[line]「バイオリズムの上昇によって、中脳辺縁系[color index="A0FF0000"]ニューロン[color index="800000"]のドーパミンが過剰分泌されたとき、ディソードは現れる」[%p]"
msgstr "27000:[name]セナ[line]Escalated biorhythms cause an overproduction of dopamine in the [color index="A0FF0000"]neurons[color index="800000"] of the mesolimbic system. That's when the Di-Sword appears.[%p]"

msgid "27100:[name]セナ[line]「それは危機的な状況や、興奮、悲しみ、憎しみ、笑いなど人それぞれだ」[%p]"
msgstr "27100:[name]セナ[line]That can happen during dangerous situations, or when you're feeling excitement, sadness, hatred, or laughter.[%p]"

msgid "27200:[name]セナ[line]「ドーパミン分泌量が多ければそれだけ観測しやすくなる」[%p]"
msgstr "27200:[name]セナ[line]The greater the amount of dopamine, the easier it becomes to observe the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "27300:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃん、そういうことなのらー」[%p]"
msgstr "27300:[name]梢[line]Yeah, that's how it works, Takumi![%p]"

msgid "27400:セナの知識の広さは異常。もしかしてとんでもなく頭いいのかも。[%p]"
msgstr "27400:Sena's knowledge was incredible. It was possible that she was incredibly smart.[%p]"

msgid "27500:っていうか、まるで“ギガロマニアックス学”でもあるかのような詳しさじゃないか。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:Actually, she knew so much that there might be an entire field of study about this. Call it “Gigalomaniacology” or something.[%p]"

msgid "27600:そもそもこんな複雑怪奇な理論や専門用語をそらで語れる女子高生なんて、日本中探してもいないんじゃないかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "27600:I could almost guarantee that no other teenage girl in Japan could talk about such complicated things and use such technical terms.[%p]"

msgid "27700:彼女はいったいどこで勉強したんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "27700:Where had she learned all this?[%p]"

msgid "27800:僕の周りには、どうしてこんなにも謎の人物ばかりが集まってくるんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "27800:Why did I keep meeting all these mysterious people?[%p]"

msgid "27900:誰か答えを提示してくれ。[%p]"
msgstr "27900:Somebody, please give me the answer.[%p]"

msgid "28000:考えるのももう疲れた。[%p]"
msgstr "28000:I'm tired of thinking.[%p]"

msgid "28100:分からないままのこんな中途半端な状態でいるのも気持ち悪い。[%p]"
msgstr "28100:It made me feel sick, knowing only a few hints, but nothing that really mattered.[%p]"

msgid "28200:だけど自分で調べる気にはならない。[linebreak]だって、みんな……普通じゃないから。[%p]"
msgstr "28200:But I didn't feel like looking into it myself. Because... none of these people were normal.[%p]"

msgid "28300:苦々しい思いを抱きつつ、溶けかけたガルガリ君の最後の一口をかじる。[%p]"
msgstr "28300:Bitterly, I took the last bite from the melted Garugari-kun popsicle.[%p]"

msgid "28400:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……。あたりだ」[%p]"
msgstr "28400:[name]拓巳[line]Huh? I won.[%p]"

msgid "28500:残った棒部分に“あたり！”という文字が刻まれていた。[linebreak]こずぴぃが戻ってきて、僕の手許をのぞき込んでくる。[%p]"
msgstr "28500:Near the bottom of the stick I could see the word “winner.” Kozupii had come back, and was now looking at the stick in my hands.[%p]"

msgid "28600:[name]梢[line]「拓巳しゃん、すーごいねー」[%p]"
msgstr "28600:[name]梢[line]Wow, Takumi![%p]"

msgid "28700:[name]セナ[line]「大した運だな」[%p]"
msgstr "28700:[name]セナ[line]You've got incredible luck.[%p]"

msgid "28800:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃん、自分も当たりが出てほしかったって羨ましがってるのら♪」[%p]"
msgstr "28800:[name]梢[line]Sena's jealous. She wanted to be a winner, too.[%p]"

msgid "28900:[name]セナ[line]「……そんなことは思っていない」[%p]"
msgstr "28900:[name]セナ[line]That's not what I was thinking.[%p]"

msgid "29000:こずぴぃ相手にそんなごまかしは通用しないと思うけど。なにしろ、考えていることを全部読まれちゃうんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "29000:I don't think you can fool Kozupii like that. She knows exactly what you're thinking.[%p]"

msgid "29100:[name]梢[line]「セナしゃんはいっつもー、当たりが出ないかなーとワクワクしながらガルガリ君を食べてるのらー」[%p]"
msgstr "29100:[name]梢[line]Sena always gets really excited whenever she eats a Garugari-kun popsicle. She hopes she'll be a winner.[%p]"

msgid "29200:[name]梢[line]「当たりを引いたのはどれくらーい？」[%p]"
msgstr "29200:[name]梢[line]How often do you win?[%p]"

msgid "29300:[name]セナ[line]「…………１割３分７厘」[%p]"
msgstr "29300:[name]セナ[line]13.7% of the time.[%p]"

msgid "29400:や、やけに細かく把握してるんだな……。[linebreak]食べるたびに計算してるってことか……。[%p]"
msgstr "29400:S-She'd calculated it really precisely. She must have kept a running tally with each one she ate.[%p]"

msgid "29500:セナもガルガリ君を食べ終わった。棒をまじまじとにらみつけ、それから小さく鼻を鳴らす。[linebreak]ハズレ、だな。あの顔は。[%p]"
msgstr "29500:Sena finished her Garugari-kun. She glared at her stick and grunted. I could tell from the look on her face that she wasn't a winner.[%p]"

msgid "29600:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あの……よ、よかったら、どうぞ……」[%p]"
msgstr "29600:[name]拓巳[line]U-Um... You can have this.[%p]"

msgid "29700:当たり棒を恐る恐る差し出す。[%p]"
msgstr "29700:I nervously offered her the winning popsicle stick.[%p]"

msgid "29800:[name]セナ[line]「他人に施しを受けるつもりはない」[%p]"
msgstr "29800:[name]セナ[line]I refuse to accept another person's generosity.[%p]"

msgid "29900:[name]セナ[line]「私は自分の可能性を試してるだけだ」[%p]"
msgstr "29900:[name]セナ[line]I'm attempting to test the limits of my own possibilities.[%p]"

msgid "30000:[name]梢[line]「でも本心では欲しーいって言ってるねー」[%p]"
msgstr "30000:[name]梢[line]But she's actually thinking that she wants it![%p]"

msgid "30100:[name]セナ[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "30100:[name]セナ[line]...[%p]"

msgid "30200:[name]拓巳[line]「あ、あげます、よ……」[%p]"
msgstr "30200:[name]拓巳[line]Y-You can have it.[%p]"

msgid "30300:[name]拓巳[line]「ぼ、僕、アイスはあんまり、た、食べないし……」[%p]"
msgstr "30300:[name]拓巳[line]I don't really eat popsicles.[%p]"

